
Overview of noun employment

The noun employment has 4 senses (first 4 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (9) employment, employ -- (the state of being employed or having a job; "they are looking for employment"; "he was in the employ of the city")
2. (9) employment, work -- (the occupation for which you are paid; "he is looking for employment"; "a lot of people are out of work")
3. (6) employment, engagement -- (the act of giving someone a job)
4. (1) use, usage, utilization, utilisation, employment, exercise -- (the act of using; "he warned against the use of narcotic drugs"; "skilled in the utilization of computers")
